Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.85,0:00:15.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么都会分崩离析 对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Things fall apart, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.82,0:00:16.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Or do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.69,0:00:19.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁还能分辨什么是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who can tell anymore what's true,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:22.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,威尔福德诡计是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}what's a Wilford ruse?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.07,0:00:26.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,于是我们紧紧抓住我们所知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So we hang on too tight to what we do know,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.54,0:00:30.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分裂为更坚固的小集团\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}crack ourselves into harder factions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.04,0:00:32.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不再害怕农业区表现欠佳\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're not afraid of our Ag-Sec failing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.87,0:00:34.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者生物安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}or Bio-Security anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.67,0:00:36.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们为威尔福德点亮红灯笼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're lighting red lanterns for Wilford
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.59,0:00:39.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们害怕彼此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}because we're afraid of each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:54.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.77,0:00:57.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在这出售仅剩的共同点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm out here selling the only common ground left.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.52,0:00:59.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都是人类\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That we're all human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.28,0:01:05.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要爱  联系以及希望的空间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know, who need love and connection and space for hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.70,0:01:08.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然我们将会自相残杀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Or we'd kill each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.46,0:01:13.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么最近的历史\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What is it about recent history
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.75,0:01:15.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都难以记住\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that's so freaking hard to remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.61,0:01:46.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永动机工程师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, Eternal Engineer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.28,0:01:49.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一直是社会工程师  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's always been a social engineer, hasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.99,0:01:50.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他必须是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He'd have to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.49,0:01:53.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他让我们都进入了他的系统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He rendered us all into his system.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.54,0:01:56.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽管他的发动机或许是永恒的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And even though his Engine may be eternal,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.33,0:02:01.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但雪国列车剩余的部分  还是需要进食\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the rest of Snowpiercer, she still runs on meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.42,0:02:06.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1034节车厢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All 1,034 cars long.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.00,0:02:26.76,特效,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\a6\c&H020202&\fs36\fn方正兰亭准黑_GBK\fsp8\t(\fsp11)\pos(192,85)}雪国列{\fsp0}车
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.00,0:02:26.76,特效,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\a6\c&H020202&\fs24\fn方正兰亭准黑_GBK\fsp8\t(\fsp11)\pos(192,166)}{\fsp3\t(\fsp4.125)}第二季 第八{\fsp0}集\N{\fsp3\t(\fsp4.125)}"永恒的工程师{\fsp0}"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.65,0:02:30.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他交代了  波吉  就跟我现在跟你谈话一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He confessed, Boki, like I'm sitting here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.11,0:02:34.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后他把他自制的杀人袋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And then he cinched his little homemade murder bag
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.11,0:02:37.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,缠在他喉咙上  试图把他的头冻掉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}around his throat, and tried to freeze his own head off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.91,0:02:40.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢这故事  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You love this story, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.08,0:02:44.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罩着他们  车尾人罩车尾人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}More cover, from a Tailie for the Tailies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.71,0:02:46.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌这故事  维修员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I hate this story, Breachman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.87,0:02:48.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不得不一直讲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But I gotta keep telling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.38,0:02:50.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得用扬声器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I gotta get on the loudspeaker
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.13,0:02:53.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向全车的人为车尾辩护  因为这是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and defend the Tail to the whole train because it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.13,0:02:53.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是他们动的手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They didn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.01,0:02:57.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想要复仇  我懂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You want revenge. I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.76,0:03:00.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你得睁大双眼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But you gotta open your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:07.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我为威尔福德卖命了30年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}30 years I risked my life for Wilford.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:10.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,30年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}30 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.86,0:03:15.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  他不会叫人杀了他的维修员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, he would not have his Breachmen killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.78,0:03:17.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波吉  缓一缓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Boki, take some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.28,0:03:19.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮我们守住中间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Help us hold the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.33,0:03:23.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴我们进行了此次会面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, I'm glad we had this meeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:25.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我们可以排除掉他了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but we can cross him off the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.13,0:03:32.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工程师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Engineer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:35.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经很久了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's been eons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:42.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她会唱歌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She can sing,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.47,0:03:44.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但她能打扫她的房间吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but can she clean her room?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:45.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放尊重点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Show some respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.52,0:03:48.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她才刚回来  你到时就明白了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The woman's just got back on her horse. You'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.98,0:03:52.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不错的延伸轨道  蒙古人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lovely stretch of track, the Mongols.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.82,0:03:56.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波状起伏  高效地形\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Undulating. Efficient terrain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.74,0:03:59.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你泡澡太多了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're bathing too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.66,0:04:00.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I beg your pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:03.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你泡澡的时候会思考\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, you think when you bathe,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.12,0:04:04.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你肯定盘算着什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so you must be up to something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:08.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡维尔工程师  如果我盘算着什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, Engineer Cavill, if I was up to something,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.71,0:04:11.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你并不需要知道  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you don't necessarily need to know about it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:14.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我注意到今早出现了一次缺口\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I noticed that there was an intentional breach this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:17.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是雪国列车  抛弃死尸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That was Snowpiercer, jettisoning the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.80,0:04:19.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是那个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nope, not that breach.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.22,0:04:22.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在这辆列车上  在我们的冷锁区里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}On this train, actually, in our cold lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.35,0:04:26.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们可能只是在测试焊接\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, they're probably just testing the seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.14,0:04:32.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前没这样过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It hasn't been like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.31,0:04:35.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四处走  我能感受到  有不能去的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Walking around, I can feel it. I got no-go zones.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.78,0:04:37.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚有很多红灯笼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There were a lot of red lanterns last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.82,0:04:39.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,车尾完全不能自由移动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Tail can't move freely at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:41.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们大多数人又回去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Most of us are right back there again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.91,0:04:43.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,车上一半的人都被洗脑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Half the train is brainwashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:45.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们失去了管道工\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We've lost the Tunnelmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.16,0:04:47.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们公开呼吁威尔福德回归\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They're openly calling for Wilford's return.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.50,0:04:50.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽管我抓了两个嫌疑人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Doesn't matter that I got two suspects behind bars.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.71,0:04:52.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们只想相信他们想相信的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}People just believe what they wanna believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.13,0:04:54.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二等厢呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What about Second Class?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.29,0:04:55.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们大多数人仍然支持你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Most of us still back you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:04:58.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中产阶级会尽力守住中间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Bourgeoisie will hold the middle long as they can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.30,0:05:01.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能这就是我们总是被坑的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's probably why we always get screwed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:03.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们是在上一站才上车的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did you all just get on at the last whistle stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.26,0:05:05.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有司闸员  你可以放松\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You've got the Brakemen, you can relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.35,0:05:06.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确定吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.56,0:05:07.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到你的一些手下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I saw some of your boys
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.56,0:05:09.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在葬礼上比划威尔福德手势\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}throwing up the Wilford horns at the funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.48,0:05:11.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是给维修员比的  是传统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, that's for the Breachmen, it's tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.35,0:05:16.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会坚守岗位  会听我的指挥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They're holding their posts. They'll follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:17.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还是不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, like, I still don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.98,0:05:19.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么不让我就待在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Like, why don't you just let me stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.32,0:05:20.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是一阵子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's only for a little time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.03,0:05:22.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里更安全  相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's much safer here. I'm telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.36,0:05:24.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小火球  闹什么脾气呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, Fireball, what's the fuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.03,0:05:25.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  我为什么一定要去前车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dad, why do I have to stay uptrain?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.91,0:05:29.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡莉  等事态平息了就好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Carly, it's just until things settle down, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.25,0:05:30.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很快就能回来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You'll be back in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.46,0:05:32.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样你离学校也近一点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This way, you'll be closer to school,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.87,0:05:35.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用每天来回跑穿过那么多节车厢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and you don't have to keep going back and forth through all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.96,0:05:40.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  知道吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's all right, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.97,0:05:41.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来抱一个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:45.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我会想你的  -我也会想你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I'm gonna miss you. - Miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:47.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了  你这样想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right. Now, look at it this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.01,0:05:49.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在保利那边可以调皮捣蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You can misbehave at the Paolis'.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:53.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但过去的路上可别逼我的司闸员用警棍对付你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just don't make my Brakeman use his nightstick on you on the way up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:05:58.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.74,0:06:04.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-希望很快会见面  -好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- See you soon. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.91,0:06:07.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:16.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情况如何\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.38,0:06:18.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们四分五裂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're divided as hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.13,0:06:21.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莱顿试图维持和平  但是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Layton's trying to keep the peace, but we're--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:24.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有人露出挑衅的表情  我们就会爆发内战\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you know, we're one dirty look away from a civil war.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.05,0:06:26.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们不相信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}People have a hard time believing
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:28.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是罗根牧师找人杀死维修队的人的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Pastor Logan had the Breachmen killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:29.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你信吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.35,0:06:33.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你对列车失去了信心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know you lost your faith on this train,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.77,0:06:35.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但对于我们那些紧紧抓着信念的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but for those of us holding on to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:38.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这事很难和解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}this one's hard to reconcile.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.65,0:06:42.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你保持信念  记得吗  我维持和平\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You keep the faith, remember? I keep the peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.58,0:06:53.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快世界末日了  宝贝  叫水管工来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The world is ending, baby! Call a plumber!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.41,0:06:54.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊  抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}God, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:06:59.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水管非得在这时候出问题吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We have to have water problems now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:01.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你希望一整天开着自动驾驶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You hoping for all-day autopilot
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.80,0:07:03.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美美地睡个午觉  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and a nice long siesta, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.67,0:07:05.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你盯紧水压\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't take your eyes off the water pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:06.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:07.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最好穿上长筒雨靴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You should probably take your wellies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.35,0:07:17.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.06,0:07:23.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请让一下  安妮  发生什么事了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Excuse me. Anne, Anne, what's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.78,0:07:26.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一开始只是我们的水龙头轻微漏水\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Started off with a tiny leak in our faucet earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.20,0:07:27.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在所有客舱都淹水了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}now all the cabins are flooding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:30.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  乘客服务部的人来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, no, here comes Hospitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:32.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在该我们上场了  小莱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, so this where we shine, LJ, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.58,0:07:34.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们表现得好  他们就不能夺走清洁部\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We do a bang-up job, they can't take Janitorial away from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.92,0:07:36.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-好  -你准备好了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Mm-hmm. - Yeah, you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.46,0:07:37.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就清洁得彻底点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's Janitor this bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:40.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们遇到大麻烦了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, you're in a pickle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.42,0:07:42.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们控制住这个车厢了  沃德尔女士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, I think this car's in hand, Ms. Wardell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.21,0:07:43.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经尽快清理了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're mopping up as fast as we can,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:45.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但有三个车厢受到影响\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but there are three cars affected.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.01,0:07:46.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-三个  -对  小莱能搞定这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Three? - Yup, LJ's on top of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.97,0:07:48.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但现在附属列车里也有水\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but there's water in the subtrain now,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:49.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您最好跟我来看看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so I think you better come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.89,0:07:51.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也这么想  走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think I better. All right, go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:53.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-祝好运  小莱  -不用担心我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Good luck, LJ. - Yeah, don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:54.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Head down this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.27,0:07:59.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我重新分布了压力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, so I'm redistributing pressure,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.81,0:08:00.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但水压仍在不断上升\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but it's still building.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.69,0:08:03.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈维  出现压力波动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Javi, I'm getting a pressure surge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.15,0:08:03.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:10.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死  我的老天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, shit! Holy mackerel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.03,0:08:12.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.12,0:08:19.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  你醒了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, goody, you're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.75,0:08:22.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被管子插过那里  感觉很不好受  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Feels awful after a tube's been down there, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.42,0:08:24.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.63,0:08:29.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你上次泡完黏糊糊之后  昏迷了挺久\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You've been out for some time since your last goo bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.26,0:08:31.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真希望海德伍德夫妇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I do wish the Headwoods would find
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.22,0:08:33.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能给这玩意起个更专业的名字  你说对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}a more scientific sounding name for the stuff, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.06,0:08:39.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:57.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,几乎不疼了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It barely hurts anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.79,0:09:02.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,流泪可能会疼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tears might hurt a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:06.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼泪里的盐分接触到新生皮肤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Salt on fresh skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.51,0:09:09.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:13.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why have you done this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.30,0:09:15.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听说你失去的那只手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I hear you've been having
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.97,0:09:18.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直感到幻痛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}phantom pain in your missing hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.47,0:09:21.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想迷惑你的大脑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I have a little trick I'd like to play on your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.31,0:09:25.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这两只是你的手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}These are your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.48,0:09:29.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.03,0:09:37.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  请相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, please, trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.83,0:09:41.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,注意力集中在你手上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Focus on your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.96,0:09:44.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看着我触碰它们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Watch me touching them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.84,0:09:48.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:52.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的大脑认为你还有手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You see, your brain believes there's still a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.68,0:09:56.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混乱的神经元群分不清真假\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A cluster of confused neurons couldn't make sense of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.68,0:10:00.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你的大脑就信以为真\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so it became fixated on your pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.32,0:10:09.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么  真的有用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What--it's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.82,0:10:13.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幻觉也有价值  如果它能带走痛苦的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Illusion has value, if it takes the pain away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.28,0:10:15.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不算太离谱的想法  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not such a far-fetched idea, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:19.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多多练习  重新组装你的大脑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Practice. Retool your brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:21.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会很有趣的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It'll be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.17,0:10:30.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不会再给你锁门了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We won't be locking your door anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.51,0:10:32.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到大爱丽丝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Welcome to Big Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.52,0:10:43.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,压强过大的现象在整趟列车上随处可见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Pressure surges are popping up all over the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.56,0:10:47.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舱门的进气口关不上  所以我们承载了太多雪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Our port intake won't close, so we're taking on too much snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.11,0:10:48.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,借过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.06,0:10:50.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把水变成氢气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Convert water to hydrogen,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.52,0:10:52.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能分流列车上的一些水储备\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}its offshoot supplies water for the train,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.24,0:10:55.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以当舱门被卡住关不上时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so when the gills are jammed open...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.07,0:10:57.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,氢气太多  水如海啸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Too much hydrogen, and a tsunami of water.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.45,0:10:59.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错  肯定是外面出了问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Exactly. It has to be external.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.45,0:11:01.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有东西卡住了舱门\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Something's jammed the gills open.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.75,0:11:04.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以手动排出过量气体\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, we can manually vent the excess,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.71,0:11:07.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那会让我们减速  这比较严重\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but that's gonna slow us down, so that's serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.46,0:11:09.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有多严重  从一到十的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How serious, scale of one to ten?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:11.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平常我会说三\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Normally, I'd call it a three.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.30,0:11:13.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们派一支维修队工人手动修复即可\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We'd send out a team of Breach workers to free it by hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.76,0:11:16.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但所有维修队工人都死了  除了波吉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But since all of our Breachmen are dead except Boki,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.30,0:11:17.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他可能拒绝修复\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}who might refuse to do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.84,0:11:19.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,严重程度是六\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Six out of ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:20.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以当作十\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We can round that up to a ten,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.85,0:11:22.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假设威尔福德与此有关\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}assuming Wilford's involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.64,0:11:24.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是所有事都与威尔福德有关\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not everything's Wilford.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.18,0:11:27.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舱门确实会被卡住  这种事会发生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Our intakes do get jammed, it happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.23,0:11:30.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博斯科维奇还在哀悼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Boscovic's still grieving.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.02,0:11:33.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得去让他冒险了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Gotta ask him to risk his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.03,0:11:37.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞快点  我们没有时间了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, make it fast. We're gonna start losing time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.66,0:11:41.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在慢了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now it's slowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.16,0:11:48.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.79,0:11:49.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是收拾得挺利落\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You clean up well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.46,0:11:51.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.71,0:11:53.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说我该过来看看这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He told me I should be here to see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.25,0:11:54.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}To see what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:11:56.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他没告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, he didn't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.72,0:11:57.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tell me what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.22,0:11:59.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,转身  亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Turn around, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.06,0:12:08.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲍勃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bob?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.66,0:12:23.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等  等等  等等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wait, wait. Wait, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.62,0:12:24.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:26.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-现在行了  -开门\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Now. - Open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.46,0:12:30.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他之前在干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What was he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.33,0:12:31.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这很严重\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is very severe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.09,0:12:38.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺住  鲍勃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on, Bob.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:43.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:45.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,维修队的老传统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}An old Breachman's tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.56,0:12:49.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么派他出去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why did you send him out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.24,0:13:01.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.46,0:13:08.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天呐  是她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My God, it's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.59,0:13:10.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听说她对凯文干了什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have you heard what she did to Kevin?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.22,0:13:15.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们从没见过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We've never actually met.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.64,0:13:19.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确实  我知道你是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Uh--no, I know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.06,0:13:22.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么来这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.10,0:13:23.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们的能耐令人惊诧  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's amazing what they can do, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.31,0:13:27.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再努努力  你就可以再次变美\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A little more effort, you could be beautiful again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.90,0:13:29.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不在乎美不美\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I-I don't give a shit about being beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.48,0:13:31.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这或许是件好事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's probably good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:36.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪国列车怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's happened on Snowpiercer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.16,0:13:37.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莱顿还在吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is Layton still standing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.45,0:13:40.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苟延残喘吧  但还在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}More like crawling, but yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.16,0:13:44.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叛逃了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You've defected.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.04,0:13:46.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回归了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.25,0:13:48.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们有非常不同的旅程\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We had very different journeys,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.21,0:13:51.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我们都曾是雪国列车的领袖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but we were both leaders on Snowpiercer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.42,0:13:55.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们花了数年对他人负责\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We spent years being responsible for others.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.01,0:13:58.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但现在我们在这\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And now that we're here,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:00.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有了那些累赘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}without all that weight,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:05.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你怎么样  但我从没睡得这么香过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know about you, but I've never slept so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.48,0:14:08.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要你想  未来就是你的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The future is yours, if you want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.65,0:14:10.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只需看看镜子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just look in the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.66,0:14:25.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你们要来了  破了那么多管子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I knew you'd be coming. All these bursting pipes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.21,0:14:27.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波吉  我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Boki, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.71,0:14:31.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们知道让你一个人出去不公平\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We know it's not fair to ask you to go out there alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.05,0:14:34.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你不想听我说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know you don't wanna hear this from me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.92,0:14:37.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但列车需要你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but the train needs you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.01,0:14:39.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,列车总是需要我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The train always needs me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.56,0:14:46.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我拒绝呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What if I say no?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.93,0:14:48.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那情况就不妙了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That would not be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.60,0:14:50.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过量吸气很严重\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}An intake's pretty serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.77,0:14:55.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是你和深渊之间的最后一个维修队工人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The last Breachworker between you and the abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.49,0:15:00.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着  我不是下来给你下令的  兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Look, I'm not down here giving you an order, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.45,0:15:02.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,决定权在你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's your call.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.46,0:15:08.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okeydokey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.25,0:15:10.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是时候去外面了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Time to go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.97,0:15:29.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乔茜  你好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hi, Josie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.69,0:15:31.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.15,0:15:34.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们给你吃了什么止痛药\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What have they given you for the pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.19,0:15:39.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我准备好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.36,0:15:45.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的使命已经完成了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've served my purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.37,0:15:47.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不不  你有更重要的使命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, no, you have a far greater purpose
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.54,0:15:49.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不是成为威尔福德的武器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}than being Wilford's weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.29,0:15:51.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我同意  他是有更重要的使命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I agree, he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.09,0:16:01.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多年来移植的人造组织\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Years of grafting synthetic tissue.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.72,0:16:04.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可怕的冻疮  和你的一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Horrible frostbite, like yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.89,0:16:06.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们重塑了他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We rebuilt him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.51,0:16:11.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而现在  我们永远也无法发现他的全部潜力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And now, we'll never discover his full potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.60,0:16:14.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要你好好休息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We need you resting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.19,0:16:18.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比以往更需要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now more than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.61,0:17:44.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有水压都在增加\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Water pressure's building at all end points.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.15,0:17:46.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,压力表进入红色区了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Pressure's in the red.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.57,0:17:47.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备好排压\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ready to vent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.45,0:17:52.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们正在排压\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They're venting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.12,0:17:54.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这很正常\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's not unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.58,0:17:56.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷淡鲍勃是想把我们分开吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Was Icy Bob trying to disconnect us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.25,0:17:58.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们慢下来了  为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They've slowed down. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.88,0:18:01.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的天呐  你怎么不直接去问他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}For pity's sake. Why don't you just ask them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.26,0:18:04.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波吉正在穿衣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Boki is getting suited up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.97,0:18:06.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要我们释放了通风口\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Once we free the intake,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.13,0:18:07.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就能逐渐提速\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we'll gradually bring her back up to speed,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.76,0:18:09.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这样会大大拖慢我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but it's gonna cost us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.51,0:18:10.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我估计要两个小时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm estimating two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.76,0:18:12.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那两小时后我们和梅在约定地方见面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's two hours later for our rendezvous with Mel,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.77,0:18:14.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经和她失联了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}who we have lost contact with.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.56,0:18:17.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保持希望\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, keep the faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.69,0:18:20.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪国列车  这里是大爱丽丝  请回话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Snowpiercer, it's Big Alice, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.90,0:18:25.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下午好  大爱丽丝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good afternoon, Big Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.07,0:18:26.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也许在好奇我们为什么减速了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're probably wondering why we've slowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.90,0:18:28.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我们要来不及接梅兰妮了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, we're going to be late picking up Melanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.95,0:18:30.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:34.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是日常维护而已\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Routine maintenance, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.58,0:18:36.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是在利用这条直线轨道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're just taking advantage of the straight track.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.96,0:18:39.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好啊  本  我们能帮忙吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, hello, Ben. Can we be of any assistance?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.13,0:18:41.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.17,0:18:42.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们很快就会进一步减速\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We'll be slowing further shortly,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.34,0:18:43.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但之后会提速的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but we'll make it up after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.84,0:18:46.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧  分秒必争\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right, then. Every second counts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.59,0:18:48.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请帮我向莱顿先生问好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do give my regards to Mr. Layton, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.30,0:18:53.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的心情非常好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's in an awful good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.47,0:18:55.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波吉到冷锁处了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Boki's in cold lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.27,0:18:58.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备行动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right, ready to roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.41,0:19:12.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-波吉  收到了吗  -收到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Boki, do you copy? - Copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.70,0:19:14.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他已经进入舱门  他在车顶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's breached the hatch. He's on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.33,0:19:17.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等你爬上梯子  我们就减速\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When you get to the ladder, we'll reduce speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.58,0:19:22.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我准备爬到侧边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay. I'm ready to go over the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.13,0:19:23.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在通风口\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's at the intake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.25,0:19:26.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将列车减速至55公里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bringing her down to 55 kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.97,0:19:33.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找到阻碍物了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I found the block.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.85,0:19:36.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个东西怎么会在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How the hell did this get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.68,0:19:37.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心  波吉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Be careful, Boki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.20,0:19:53.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我够不着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I cannot reach it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.37,0:20:00.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷静\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.25,0:20:04.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,淡定点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, okay, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.43,0:20:18.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波吉  怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Boki, what's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.02,0:20:20.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波吉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Boki?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.98,0:20:24.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拿到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.40,0:20:25.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他拿到了  -太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- He's got it. - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.73,0:20:27.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm coming home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.82,0:20:31.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要回家了  我要回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm coming home! I'm coming home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.36,0:20:33.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-干得漂亮  -我要回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Good work. - I'm coming home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.11,0:20:34.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们把他带回来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's get him back inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.97,0:20:46.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,威尔福德十号  这不是意外\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Number Ten Wilford. This was no accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.23,0:20:50.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你怎么知道  -入口阶梯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- How do you know? - The access ladder.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.69,0:20:52.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阶梯旁的冰碎了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ice was broken off the rungs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:55.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人在我之前下去过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Somebody went down before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.95,0:21:00.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们去检查一下水平\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's go check the levels. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:09.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是威尔福德自己给我的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wilford gave me this himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.29,0:21:10.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He said,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.25,0:21:13.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,维修队的人为我冒了生命危险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Breachmen risk their lives for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,0:21:16.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}With this,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:19.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我保证也会为你们去冒生命危险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I pledge the same to you."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:24.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿着吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.64,0:21:31.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许有一天你可以拿这个去堵住他的嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Maybe you can shove it up his ass one day?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.98,0:21:32.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.23,0:21:38.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会在发动机服务器机房做些检测\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We'll run some tests in the engine server room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.19,0:21:39.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-出了什么事  -稍等一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- What-- what's going on? - Give us a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.65,0:21:41.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-谁...  -我把列车调至自动驾驶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Who-- - I put the train on autopilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.28,0:21:44.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事  你的人吓到我了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, what's that? Your boy's scaring me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.66,0:21:45.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.99,0:21:48.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们把地毯拉了起来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We've pulled up the carpet
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.16,0:21:49.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打扫了所有住所\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and mopped out all the residences.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.79,0:21:51.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们只需调高供热通风与空气调节\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now we'll just turn the HVAC on high
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.62,0:21:52.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让它们都干掉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and let them all dry out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.92,0:21:54.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们好努力  小莱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're trying very hard, LJ.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.17,0:21:58.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  为了威尔福德的列车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, we are. For Wilford's train.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:01.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以不管事情如何发展  你都可以依赖我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So however things fall, you can count on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.38,0:22:04.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会发生什么的  小莱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nothing's going to fall, Lj.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.22,0:22:06.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只需继续好好干活就行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You just keep up the good work.
