Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.67,0:36:00.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让开  别挡道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Move, get out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.95,0:36:01.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What the hell's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.28,0:36:05.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手动重启  从来没有过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A manual restart? That's never been done before.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.56,0:36:06.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有听到安德烈的消息吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have you heard anything from Andre?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.98,0:36:07.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.80,0:36:10.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传言威尔福德在前车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Word got out Wilford is uptrain.
