Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.56,0:36:16.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听到  你要关掉雪国列车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, you're powering down Snowpiercer.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.26,0:36:18.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.19,0:36:19.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-这是你计划的一部分吗  -不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Is this a part of your plan? - No!
