Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.21,0:38:32.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好  很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good, good, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.56,0:38:45.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个接一个的游戏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Games upon games.
