Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.17,0:41:24.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}闪光信号
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.67,0:42:09.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们要带你去大爱丽丝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They're taking you to Big Alice.
